{"tid":1657426,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【HKCC 舊生和同學 必入 幫手】陳偉強講師謊話連篇 為人不誠實","createTime":"2019-10-16T05:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:15:28.000Z","uid":216899,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12717915c1d14d75ec378a5d5237dce6b4581021","tid":1657426,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"呢位講師<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人品絕對有問題</span></strong></span> 請香港人唔好相信佢嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n背景：陳偉強教modern china同中西溝 經常奶共 藍到變黑<br />\n<br />\n事緣：佢以學校講師身份接受東網訪問 話學生係暴徒 於是10月8日學生喺tutorial圍堵強仔 要求為東網事件現身說法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">問題1：以學校老師身份接受訪問 不信任及冤枉學生</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTutorial時佢再話學生係暴徒、非法集結、非法禁錮佢<br />\n<br />\n東網Link：<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191005/bkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191005%2Fbkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVruZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=4364df5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191005/bkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">問題2：立即報警 不願和學生溝通</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢未能走出課室 於是越過學校保安直接報警 因此當日一直2架EU滿綠狗喺HKCC<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>問題3：<span style=\"color: purple;\">【最嚴重】自己跌親 卻聲稱學生推跌自己</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢唔小心跌左三次 但就話學生推跌佢 當日好多同學直播全程 完全冇見到學生推跌佢<br />\nGif：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKVewER.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKVewER.gif&h=3b269bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">問題4：濫用醫療服務 有得走又唔走</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由於校方阻止警察進入校園 佢就叫救護車 但佢咩事都冇 濫用急救服務<br />\n<br />\n急救問佢走唔走 佢選擇唔走 話只有警察可以保護到佢安全 要警察護送佢走 最後又話學生非法禁錮佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>問題5：<span style=\"color: brown;\">誣衊好心幫自己的學校院長</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n院長曾經去到現場調解 俾過落台階佢 但佢唔接受 佢仲話院長唔俾警察進入校園 妨礙司法公正<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">問題6：缺席學校交流會</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n學校喺10月9日搞一個交流會 根據部分同學口供 佢本人話會出席 院長都話有叫佢出席<br />\n<br />\n最後佢冇出現 連朝早堂都取消左 但佢就走去接受CCTVB同支那01 採訪 聲稱學生禁錮佢五個鐘 又話學生推跌佢三次<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB：<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/local/5d9db762e6038394077b1fd9/香港專上學院有講師就反蒙面法表態-遭學生圍困近五小時\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d9db762e6038394077b1fd9%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E6%9C%89%E8%AC%9B%E5%B8%AB%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B-%E9%81%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%9B%B0%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVruZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=5fc7dc58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/local/5d9db762e6038394077b1fd9/香港專上學院有講師就反蒙面法表態-遭學生圍困近五小時</a><br />\n支那01：<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=Tr7Yxd7YJZc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTr7Yxd7YJZc&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVruZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=f1717bdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=Tr7Yxd7YJZc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">個人意見 不代表所有學生</span><br />\n我同幾個同學討論過幾次 我地都覺得學校老師會有不同嘅政治立場 唔會專登去探究 更會互相尊重 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果老師並非出言不遜 同學都唔會咁大反應</span></span><br />\n<br />\n問題起源係：<br />\n陳偉強使用學校老師身份去接受訪問 影響學校形象 同時亦顯示佢不信任學生<br />\n<br />\n而佢當日冇回答同學問題 選擇直接報警 到依家都不斷接受親政府媒體嘅訪問 冇面對過學生 好多學生都感到好失望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">暴專人 推爆佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a097d1c51711884d30db3886b769d642bbbc4f4e","tid":1657426,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n釋放強強"},{"pid":"236db519fbbddff3871068373b5a42083b0d6a87","tid":1657426,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"釋放強仔"},{"pid":"b51187e92e508027f5f3d6def9f998839246d44a","tid":1657426,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"釋放陳偉強"},{"pid":"e1bf1b3f725700cb3eee8cd3407ac00eb0f9068c","tid":1657426,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96c18e9e2a17de3277f7eb253821c6ac472534be","tid":1657426,"uid":332494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12717915c1d14d75ec378a5d5237dce6b4581021","tid":1657426,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"呢位講師<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人品絕對有問題</span></strong></span> 請香港人唔好相信佢嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n背景：陳偉強教modern china同中西溝 經常奶共 藍到變黑<br />\n<br />\n事緣：佢以學校講師身份接受東網訪問 話學生係暴徒 於是10月8日學生喺tutorial圍堵強仔 要求為東網事件現身說法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">問題1：以學校老師身份接受訪問 不信任及冤枉學生</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTutorial時佢再話學生係暴徒、非法集結、非法禁錮佢<br />\n<br />\n東網Link：<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191005/bkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191005%2Fbkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVruZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=4364df5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191005/bkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">問題2：立即報警 不願和學生溝通</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢未能走出課室 於是越過學校保安直接報警 因此當日一直2架EU滿綠狗喺HKCC<br />\n